{"tid":61243,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"人一世物一世煙仔係一定要食一次","createTime":"2016-12-31T05:52:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-01T15:08:38.000Z","uid":51346,"like":4,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"18b56025069da335a7b43e5589398e9bca0c6783","tid":61243,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T05:52:24.000Z","msg":"一手煙同你平時食嗰啲二手煙其實感覺好唔同 人一世物一世點都要試返支<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />定力夠一定唔會上癮<br />\n但記得唔好浪費錢去買 反正你都係食一支咁大把<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n身邊有朋友食煙嘅 咪問佢借支食吓囉<br />\n佢唔肯嘅 咪問佢借一啖食囉 一啖肯啦掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：無朋友 依家一路行 一路搵緊地下有冇食剩嘅煙仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c83783d4e9b4f759b10cc755980f5451e3ce9de","tid":61243,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T05:52:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"577267d6efb52588f5474a3c33a1c32c76ad688f","tid":61243,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T05:53:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a357b597671ce856b62ddaac914976510929eb2e","tid":61243,"uid":20963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T05:54:27.000Z","msg":"臭到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n吱左兩淡就掉左"},{"pid":"e08c610a116a54f112eb5b33b21c59ec598f466d","tid":61243,"uid":29224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T05:55:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d713b867f81ab53c0a779d2bbef7a15297dec23c","tid":61243,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T05:56:00.000Z","msg":"<blockqu